<inglise> Whereas Council Regulation (EEC) No 2358/71 of 26 October 1971 on the common organization of the market in seeds (3), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1167/77 (4), provided for the granting, under certain conditions, of a. production aid for seeds; whereas the granting of this aid is decided each year for the marketing year beginning in the following year; </inglise>
